"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/221214_7fffb663120dd173020ed4b9bc223583.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F221214_7fffb663120dd173020ed4b9bc223583.jpg&h=36e138bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d0f8590efc6cead411deb59f2eed4949068a563","tid":760020,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T18:46:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk&d=NOp1Vkza2C8DAO0UI1TKxG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=788e349d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk</a>主持鍾晴嫌工廠狗污糟-言論被斥教壞人-其後fb發文道歉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/742252\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/742252</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"46a258edee5cdfbd490e90f0f4247ed1fa30d9bb","tid":760020,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T18:51:44.000Z","msg":"隻狗係大陸實死無生"},{"pid":"45e0db50e86c3482855df620e9dfa5ee2d3e1324","tid":760020,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T18:57:07.000Z","msg":"人類朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5dda23f4097b83702e3bff46b5891f0a7c51adb","tid":760020,"uid":82940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T18:59:58.000Z","msg":"屌 細個比仆街狗追過 跑撚左成70米佢個閪主人先出現嗌走佢"},{"pid":"558773b9e71044e6eb6484042e4334a714b3a17e","tid":760020,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:39:49.000Z","msg":"台灣人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f663b7cac466d4704e7f117525f24e12dae561","tid":760020,"uid":57968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:45:10.000Z","msg":"應該平時少做運動，一下子跑咁耐又無水份補充，心肺負荷唔到就咁失救"}]}